* 02_solvate.inp
* Solvate the minimized protein in a cubic TIP3P water box
*

stream toppar/toppar.str

open read card unit 30 name protein.psf
read psf card unit 30

open read card unit 40 name protein_min.crd
read coor card unit 40

! Box dimensions (edit to fit your system, Angstroms)
set boxsize 70.0

! Read a pre-equilibrated water box and overlay
open read card unit 11 name toppar/water_box.crd
read sequence tip3 8000
generate WT00 noangle nodihedral

open read card unit 12 name toppar/water_box.crd
read coor card unit 12 append

! Delete waters overlapping the protein (within 2.6 A)
delete atom sele .byres. (segid WT00 .and. type OH2 .and. -
    (.not. segid WT00 .around. 2.6)) end

! Center system and set up periodic boundaries
coor stat
crystal define cubic @boxsize @boxsize @boxsize 90.0 90.0 90.0
crystal build cutoff 14.0
image byres xcen 0.0 ycen 0.0 zcen 0.0 sele segid WT00 end

energy

open write card unit 50 name protein_solv.psf
write psf card unit 50

open write card unit 51 name protein_solv.crd
write coor card unit 51
* Solvated coordinates
*

stop
